	   <tr><td colspan=2>The experience penalty on all hybrid classes was removed a good part of a year ago.&nbsp;&nbsp;All classes level at the same rate, with the only exceptions being warriors and rogues levelling slightly faster (lord knows why).<br><br>Since I'm short on time this morning, I'll leave you with one tip on being a paladin:  Use your head when you're using your spells.  There are a lot of minor uses that aren't apparent right away but are of extreme use to groups.<br>&nbsp;<br><b>Praetor</b>, 60th Crusader<br>Avatars of Discord</td></tr>
