	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you're on an older server that is primarily populated by players just power-levling an alternate character (i.e. no 'true' newbies), then I could see this happening.&nbsp;&nbsp;Under those circumstances you may want to choose a different character or play on a different (newer) server.<br><br>Now before everyone jumps down my throat about endorsing quitting and telling this guy to stick it out and such, remember that we play this game to have fun.  As much as I like playing a paladin I'm not on some holy crusade to prove to people that the paladin class is 'legit'.  Paladins are best in groups and soloing is a tough road.  If you aren't able to find groups without a huge hassle, then yes, you might enjoy your time more with another class.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
