	   <tr><td colspan=2>Cease lvl 9<br>Desist lvl 15<br><br>Both are sold in the cleric/paladin guild in shadowhaven.....neither are TRUE stuns though (the mob doesnt pause atttacks for any amount of time) both spells are &quot;interrupts&quot; (like trying to bash a caster with no damage though)<br>you can also purchace these others from the same merchant:<br><br>Instrument of Nife lvl 30<br>Divine Vigor lvl 39<br>Valor of Marr lvl 49&nbsp;&nbsp; <br><br>the rest of our SoL spells are drops off mobs in certain zones:<br><br>Thunder of Karana lvl 49 drops in Fungi<br>Words of Tranquility lvl 54 drops in Fungi<br>Breath of Tunare lvl 56 drops in Maidens Eye<br>Healing Wave of Prexus lvl 58 drops in Maidens Eye<br>Remove Greater Curse lvl 60<br>Brell's Mountainous Barrier lvl 60<br>&nbsp;<br>Ryanlynx<br>Paladin of Mith Marr<br>Xev<br><br>"Honor before Humility and all that jazz."</td></tr>
