	   <tr><td colspan=2>Congrats on your player choice Kalvin. Enchanters are indeed awesome and much needed...especially at higher levels. Crowd control becomes absolutely necessary as you continue to level.<br><br>One thing to keep in mind, just so you are ready for it when it happens, enchanters die...ALOT!!&nbsp;&nbsp;Multiple mobs come into camp, the Echanter mezzes them, the group is trying to kill them all and someone breaks mez.  Guess who the mob comes to?  That's right...the Enchanter!  And since the Enchanter is wearing little more than tissue paper for armor...they die.  They die alot.  Just get ready for it. Otherwise, Enchanters are a GREAT class and have some very nifty abilities and are definitely popular with groups.<br><br>Good luck!!<br><br>Kneesmasher Ayebulger<br>Dwarven Cavalier<br><br>&quot;Never Mistake Kindness for Weakness&quot;<br>&nbsp;<br>Kneesmasher Ayebulger<br>Dwarven Knight<br>Torvonnilous Server<br><br>"Never Mistake Kindness for Weakness"</td></tr>
